    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is absolutely pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a complete service history to prove its meticulous upkeep. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
