    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this great value! This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go reliably. While it shows some honest signs of its journey with visible wear and tear inside and out, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable ride at a budget-friendly price. It's a hardworking car that still has plenty of life left to offer!",
